;;;;USER-INTERFACE:     NONE
;;;;DESCRIPTION
;;;;    
;;;;    Pre-processes rst files.  New directives implemented:
;;;;
;;;;       .. include:: path.rst
;;;;
;;;;           The contents of the file at path is included (and
;;;;           processed).
